Explode.Description: This action is used to explode a line further to display all the explode details specified in the Line Attribute Explode.
Explode.Name: Explode

Field Down.Description: This action is used to position the cursor vertically to the next field.
Field Down.Name: Field Down

Field Next.Description: This action is used to position the cursor horizontally to the next field.
Field Next.Name: Field Next

Field Prev.Description: This action is used to position the cursor horizontally to he previous field.
Field Prev.Name: Field Prev

Field Up.Description: This action is used to the position the cursor vertically to the previous field.
Field Up.Name: Field Up

Toggle Selection.Description: This action is used to select or deselect a line.
Toggle Selection.Name: Toggle Selection
